<table border="0" cellpadding="5" width="550" cellspacing="5" height="400" >
<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; direction: rtl;">שלום&nbsp;{!Task.CreatedBy},</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; direction: rtl;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; direction: rtl;">ישנה משימה שיצרת ה<span style="font-size: 12pt;">עומדת לעבור את זמן הטיפול בה!</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; direction: rtl;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; direction: rtl;">אם המשימה לא נוצרה על ידך יש לבצע בדיקה עם <b>{!Task.Agent_assigned_name__c}</b>&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 12pt;">לגביי השלמתה</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; direction: rtl;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; direction: rtl;">אם יצרת את המשימה - יש לבצעה!</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; direction: rtl;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; direction: rtl;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; direction: rtl;">למעבר ישיר למשימה יש ללחוץ</div><div style="direction: rtl;"><font face="arial">{!Task.URL_Task__c}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; direction: rtl;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; direction: rtl;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; direction: ltr;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; direction: ltr;"><br></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>